{"tid":2256470,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"仲講鬼滅之刃？","createTime":"2020-10-24T11:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T11:52:25.000Z","uid":312648,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd90e6fb210a1d8ffbfe16198803a374106d89e","tid":2256470,"uid":312648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"今季咒術迥戰屌打你啦<br />\n鬼滅之刃剩係得第19集好睇, 前面差唔多睇到瞓着<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咒術迥戰so far淨係出咗四集, 已經差唔多打足4集, 除咗經費之外, 作畫分鏡動作流暢度全部拍得住鬼滅 ep19<br />\n<br />\n兩套嘢嘅主角數量都係三、四個人, 但係呢邊嘅虎杖比炭治郎更有個人特色, 例如虎杖同佢阿爺之間種內斂含蓄嘅大男人感情, 又唔會好似扮鬼臉尻下尻下個種嘅搞笑, 劇情輕鬆同緊湊會放埋同一集, 加埋首chill到爆嘅片尾曲, 每一集睇完幾次都好似意猶未盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其係第四集啦<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔明鬼滅有咩咁好吹奏, 都過咗成年, 點解唔吹奏下今季嘅神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a733d260e691dfb096fc31f710ad8175d75d35bf","tid":2256470,"uid":152542,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"根本冇人吹奏<br />\n係套野多人睇你班連登仔唔抵得係咁屌咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70eeafe8243f9e82a468c371f559285f1d007dc","tid":2256470,"uid":312648,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:37:26.000Z","msg":"咒術迥戰下既 東京<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQu1EVb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQu1EVb.png&h=b464e47e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f36b786ca5636c720aa9b6f78e2d741e62c25ae","tid":2256470,"uid":255150,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7cd90e6fb210a1d8ffbfe16198803a374106d89e","tid":2256470,"uid":312648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"今季咒術迥戰屌打你啦<br />\n鬼滅之刃剩係得第19集好睇, 前面差唔多睇到瞓着<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\"